{
  "verses": [
    {
      "verse_num": 1,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "Then said he unto the disciples,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 5,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "Increase our faith.",
          "speaker": "Apostles"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 6,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And the Lord said,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 11,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And it came to pass, as he went to Jerusalem, that he passed through the midst of Samaria and Galilee."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": [
        "Jesus Travels to Jerusalem"
      ]
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 12,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And as he entered into a certain village, there met him ten men that were lepers, which stood afar off:"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 13,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "Jesus, Master, have mercy on us.",
          "speaker": "Lepers"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 14,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And when he saw them, he said unto them,"
        },
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And it came to pass that, as they went, they were cleansed."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 15,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And one of them, when he saw that he was healed, turned back, and with a loud voice glorified God,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 16,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And fell down on his face at his feet, giving him thanks: and he was a Samaritan."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 17,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And Jesus answering said,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 19,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And he said unto him,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 20,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And when he was demanded of the Pharisees, when the kingdom of God should come, he answered them and said,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": [
        "The Kingdom of God"
      ]
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 22,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And he said unto the disciples,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 37,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "Where, Lord?",
          "speaker": "Disciples"
        },
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And he said unto them,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    }
  ]
}